Free-floating Anxiety or General Anxiety Disorder is the most common type of anxiety disorder. It is a stress disorder that is caused when you are nervous, confused, or worried about an uncertain outcome. This might seem normal at first because almost all of us feel like this before a big day at work, an interview, and a doctor’s appointment. This feeling is normal and okay too. But, if these feelings overpower your thoughts and affect your mood and life more than required, then this is what free-floating anxiety is. 

CBD, a safe cannabinoid has been shown to reduce stress and lower the symptoms of free-floating anxiety naturally. This is because CBD targets the endocannabinoid system of our body that is responsible to regulate our moods and other important physiological and cognitive functions. CBD is also effective against a large variety of disorders and their symptoms that include muscle aches, sore muscles, viral infections, psychosis, anxiety, depression, seizures, and spasms. So, if you inculcate CBD in your life, and exercise, eat healthy food, and give yourself the appropriate time, there is a certain chance to end free-floating anxiety naturally within a few months.
